          </p>
          <p>
            You can also click the 'Legge Translation' button to view the translations of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Legge"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-link"></span> James Legge</a>, a Scottish sinologist. His translations were chosen over numerous and various others.
          </p>
